resdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/7jI_6c8xRzo/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2025-07-02\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.5,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"A new era of dinosaurs begins as humanity struggles to coexist with the prehistoric giants.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,878],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"7jI_6c8xRzo\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"125m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"A fresh start for the franchise that returns to the wonder and terror of the original films. Scarlett Johansson leads a stellar cast in a survival thriller that doesn't hold back.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":7,\\\"title\\\":\\\"The Mandalorian \\u0026 Grogu\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/t8f_Wp2S1_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/t8f_Wp2S1_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2026-05-22\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8.4,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Din Djarin and Grogu take their adventures to the big screen.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,878],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"t8f_Wp2S1_o\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"118m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"The beloved duo makes a grand leap to cinemas. The scale is epic, but the heart of the story remains the bond between a hunter and his foundling. A must-watch for Star Wars fans.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":8,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Toy Story 5\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/X_zQo-QhA0Y/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/X_zQo-QhA0Y/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2026-06-19\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.8,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Woody, Buzz, and the gang reunite for a new chapter in their lives.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[16,12,35,10751],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"X_zQo-QhA0Y\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"100m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Pixar somehow finds new emotional ground to cover with these iconic characters. A poignant reflection on friendship and the passage of time, wrapped in a fun adventure.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":9,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EGo6rXjA_zY/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EGo6rXjA_zY/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2026-06-26\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8.1,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Kara Zor-El travels the galaxy to find her own identity and become a hero.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,878],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"EGo6rXjA_zY\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"130m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Grounded in a space-epic aesthetic, this film introduces a Supergirl that is both powerful and vulnerable. A standout entry in the new DCU.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":10,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Masters of the Universe\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/5qV8XvR9y_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/5qV8XvR9y_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2026-06-05\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.6,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"He-Man must defend Eternia from the evil forces of Skeletor.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,14],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"5qV8XvR9y_o\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"122m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"A high-fantasy epic that finally gives He-Man the big-screen treatment he deserves. The production design is spectacular, bringing Eternia to life in vivid detail.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":11,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Moana 2\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hXz3m6Z2Z_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hXz3m6Z2Z_o/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-27\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Moana sets sail on a new voyage to the far seas of Oceania.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[16,12,35,10751],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"hXz3m6Z2Z_o\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"108m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Disney delivers another magical musical adventure. The chemistry between Moana and Maui remains the highlight, set against breathtaking oceanic vistas.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":12,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Mufasa: The Lion King\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/o17MF9WkSRE/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/o17MF9WkSRE/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-12-20\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.4,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"The origin story of the legendary Pride Rock king.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,18,10751],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"o17MF9WkSRE\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"115m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Barry Jenkins brings his poetic touch to the Pride Lands. This prequel offers a nuanced look at the rise of Mufasa and his relationship with Taka (Scar).\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":13,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Sonic the Hedgehog 3\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/qSu6i2iFKN0/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/qSu6i2iFKN0/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-12-20\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8.2,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Sonic, Tails, and Knuckles face off against a new threat: Shadow.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,35,10751],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"qSu6i2iFKN0\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"110m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"The franchise continues its winning streak with the introduction of Shadow. The action is faster, and the stakes are higher than ever before.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":14,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Gladiator II\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/4L6p-8Qv68k/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/4L6p-8Qv68k/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-22\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.7,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Years after the death of Maximus, Lucius enters the Colosseum.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,18],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"4L6p-8Qv68k\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"148m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Ridley Scott returns to the arena with an epic scope. Paul Mescal is riveting as Lucius, capturing the legacy of the first film while carving his own path.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":15,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Wicked\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/6COmYeLsz4c/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/6COmYeLsz4c/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-22\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8.5,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"The untold story of the witches of Oz.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[14,10402,10749],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"6COmYeLsz4c\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"160m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Cynthia Erivo and Ariana Grande are spectacular in this faithful and grand adaptation. A visual feast that honors the beloved stage musical.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":16,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Paddington in Peru\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/L6P3nI6V_Is/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/L6P3nI6V_Is/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-08\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"Paddington travels to Peru to visit his Aunt Lucy.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[12,35,10751],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"L6P3nI6V_Is\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"103m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Our favorite bear returns in another heartwarming and hilarious adventure. The shift to the Amazon brings a fresh energy and wonderful new characters.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":17,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Red One\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/wL7vMId5Y5I/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/wL7vMId5Y5I/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-15\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":6.8,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"A polar bounty hunter must rescue Santa Claus.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,12,35,14],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"wL7vMId5Y5I\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"123m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"A high-octane holiday adventure that blends action and mythology. The Rock and Chris Evans have great chemistry in this unique Christmas caper.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":18,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Elevation\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/XgJcRmsT1C0/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/XgJcRmsT1C0/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-11-08\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":7.1,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"A single father and two women venture from safety to face monstrous creatures to save a young boy's life.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[28,878,53],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"XgJcRmsT1C0\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"100m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"A tense, post-apocalyptic thriller with a strong core of survival. Anthony Mackie delivers a grounded performance in a world filled with danger.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":19,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Nosferatu\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/nur0rOPr6QA/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/nur0rOPr6QA/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-12-25\\\",\\\"vote_average\\\":8.7,\\\"overview\\\":\\\"A gothic tale of obsession between a haunted young woman and the terrifying vampire infatuated with her.\\\",\\\"genre_ids\\\":[14,27],\\\"trailer_id\\\":\\\"nur0rOPr6QA\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"UHD 4K\\\",\\\"duration\\\":\\\"135m\\\",\\\"review_content\\\":\\\"Robert Eggers creates a chillingly beautiful masterwork. Bill Skarsgård's portrayal of Count Orlok is haunting, and the atmosphere is thick with dread. A horror classic in the making.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":20,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Better Man\\\",\\\"poster_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/K0tA8W5m-hY/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"backdrop_path\\\":\\\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/K0tA8W5m-hY/maxresdefault.jpg\\\",\\\"release_date\\\":\\\"2024-12-25\\\",\\\"vote_aver